    "originContent": "> Based on [@sveltekit/adapter-static](https://github.com/sveltejs/kit/blob/master/packages/adapter-static). Credit goes to [these people](https://github.com/sveltejs/kit/graphs/contributors) for their hard work to make Svelte so great",
    "translatedContent": "> 基于 [@sveltekit/adapter-static](https://github.com/sveltejs/kit/blob/master/packages/adapter-static)。感谢 [这些人](https://github.com/sveltejs/kit/graphs/contributors) 的辛勤付出，让 Svelte 变得如此出色。"
  },
