    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "为 SPA 模式指定回退页面，例如 `index.html`、`200.html` 或 `404.html`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "qT2GxSu9t71kiO1KFphiUg1BGUmnyJTIIiCh3F+raHM=",
    "originContent": "Specify a fallback page for SPA mode, e.g. `index.html` or `200.html` or `404.html`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### precompress"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "Ps44qpJ341rqTjP+pRhVNPISQks68ljiSk1QRhaHbYw=",
    "originContent": "### precompress",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "如果为 `true`，则使用 brotli 和 gzip 对文件进行预压缩。这将生成 `.br` 和 `.gz` 文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "xZYtIMz8mslSHt9dfc+qylsCKcWD5omIEIvf2szWSV0=",
    "originContent": "If `true`, precompresses files with brotli and gzip. This will generate `.br` and `.gz` files.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### manifest"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "aNS9+y4FmJPnf1/DFmwL7xMd0/JGUp74bk4655Zkbyg=",
    "originContent": "### manifest",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "如果您想为不同目标平台使用不同的清单文件，请指定清单文件名，例如 `chrome_manifest.json`、`firefox_manifest.json`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "6nn0eq2bFjU+EcuHCtIWlwHEHZiUOIWk1En2Iri+y7o=",
    "originContent": "Specify manifest file name if you want different manifests for different target platforms, e.g. `chrome_manifest.json`, `firefox_manifest.json`.",
    "translatedContent": "此文件名必须与 `static` 目录（包含您的静态文件的目录）中存在的文件名匹配。所选的目标文件将在构建目录中重命名为 `manifest.json`，所有其他名称中包含 `manifest` 的 `.json` 文件将不会被复制。"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "j/KHAzHBVLRFJ6TGeLWKgd2XbyHonuHR2ciUo/V+0fk=",
    "originContent": "This file name must match one that is present in the `static` directory (the dir containing your static files). The selected target file will be renamed to `manifest.json` in the build directory, and all other `.json` files with `manifest` in the name won't be copied.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
